<!-- Phase 212.O.3 — board-agnostic run_plan launch file.

     Single-node launch consumed IDENTICALLY by both
     `posix_entry/build.rs` and `freertos_entry/build.rs`. The
     `nros-build::generate_run_plan` emit must be byte-identical
     across the two Entry pkgs since codegen depends only on the
     launch XML + the nros-build version — never the Board impl. -->
